1. *Toliki* broj ljudi nije mogao da stane u autobus. (Such a large number of people couldn't fit in the bus.)
2. Bio sam iznenađen *tolikom* količinom hrane koju su doneli. (I was surprised by the amount of food they brought.)
3. Da li je moguće da je cijena *toliko* porasla za samo nekoliko dana? (Is it possible that the price has increased so much in just a few days?)
4. *Tolikog* psa nikada nisam vidio u svom životu. (I have never seen such a big dog in my life.)
5. Čekao sam *toliko* dugo da sam skoro zaboravio zašto sam tu. (I waited so long that I almost forgot why I was there.)
6. *Toliki* značaj ima ova tema da moramo razgovarati o njoj. (This topic is so important that we must talk about it.)
7. *Toliko sam* se umorio da ne mogu ni hodati. (I am so tired that I can't even walk.)
8. Nikada nisam vidio *tolike* gužve u gradu. (I have never seen such crowds in the city.)
9. *Tolika* količina kiše je napravila veliku štetu usevima. (Such a large amount of rain caused a lot of damage to the crops.)
10. Bila je *tolika* tama da nisam mogao ništa da vidim. (It was so dark that I couldn't see anything.)